.SH NAME
modecpy \- Prepare response for MODE SENSE
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" modecpy
.BI "(u8 *dest "  ","
.BI "const u8 *src "  ","
.BI "int n "  ","
.BI "bool changeable "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "dest" 12
output buffer
.IP "src" 12
data being copied
.IP "n" 12
length of mode page
.IP "changeable" 12
whether changeable parameters are requested

Generate a generic MODE SENSE page for either current or changeable
parameters.

